nodes.text: Axel Dench played Merumeru in Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith. Also in his career he has starred in films such as Bill & Ted's Excellent Adventure, Flight of the Navigator, Twins and hit TV series Grange Hill

Dench, who stands at 6'11" and weighs 243 lbs, has also played professional basketball in Australia's National Basketball League for the Wollongong Hawks and Melbourne Tigers. He currently works in Fund Settlements for La Trobe Financial in Melbourne, Australia.
